# Project Vision

## Purpose

The purpose of the Clementine's Pet Spa Management System is to provide a modern, user-friendly web application for a fictional locally owned pet grooming business.

The application will allow customers to learn about the business, explore available grooming services, schedule appointments, contact the business, and apply for employment opportunities through an intuitive online experience.

In addition to serving customers, the application will provide tools for business management, allowing staff to organize customer information, manage pets, schedule appointments, maintain service offerings, and support day-to-day operations.

---

## Vision Statement

Create a professional, reliable, and scalable web application that demonstrates modern software engineering practices while providing an enjoyable experience for both customers and business staff.

The system should be easy to use, maintainable, and capable of growing as new features and business needs are introduced.

---

## Target Users

The application is designed for two primary groups of users:

### Customers

Customers can:

- Learn about the business
- Browse available grooming services
- Schedule appointments
- Contact the business
- Submit employment applications

### Business Staff

Business staff can:

- Manage customer information
- Manage pet records
- Manage appointments
- Manage employees
- Manage grooming services

---

## Project Goals

The project aims to:

- Improve the customer experience by providing convenient online services.
- Organize business information in a structured and efficient manner.
- Demonstrate professional software design and development practices.
- Serve as a foundation for future enhancements and additional functionality.

---

## Success Criteria

The project will be considered successful when it:

- Provides an intuitive user experience.
- Accurately manages business data.
- Supports the primary needs of customers and staff.
- Is organized using clean, maintainable software architecture.
- Can be expanded with new features as the business grows.
